Package org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.web

This package contains java beans and supporting classes for driving the web app ui.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AeAbstractAdminBean Base class to provide access to IAeEngineAdministration.
AeAbstractListingBean Provides common methods for displaying "scrollable" rows on web page.
AeAlarmListingBean Wraps the details for the Message Receivers Queue listing.
AeCatalogItemDetailBean Bean for displaying the details of a wsdl deployment.
AeCatalogItemType Simple class for wrapping a type for display in catalog filter.
AeCatalogListingBean Used for displaying the top level wsdl deployments listing.
AeDeployedProcessesBean Wraps the AeProcessDeploymentDetail array for the deployed processes listing.
AeDeployedServicesBean Wraps the AeServiceDeploymentInfo array for the deployed services listing.
AeDeploymentLogsBean Wraps the deployment logs listing and allows access to a single log file via its name.
AeEngineConfigBean Bean for driving display of home page.
AeEngineStatusBean Bean for driving display of home page.
AeInboundReceiveDetailBean This bean controls the display of queued receives - either unmatched or message receivers depending on how the bean is configured.
AeInboundReceivesBean Top level listing of unmatched inbound queued receives.
AeJavaTypesWrapper Exposes well known java types via bean propery accessors.
AeMessageReceiverDetailWrapper Wraps single AeMessageReceiver for bean access.
AeMessageReceiversListingBean Wraps the details for the Message Receivers Queue listing.
AePartnerDefLinkTypeBean This bean is used by the admin console when the popup info window is shown for a single partner def's partner link type.
AePartnerDefsBean Wraps the partner definitions listing.
AePartnerDetailBean Wraps the info for a specific pdef.
AePartnerDetailWrapper Wraps the details of a pdef row.
AeProcessDeploymentSelectorBean Bean for selecting the info on a specific process deployment.
AeProcessInstanceDetailWrapper Wraps an AeProcessInstanceDetail object and provides bean accessors for ui client.
AeProcessListingBean Controls the filtering/display of active process details.
AeProcessPruningBean Bean for driving display of process pruning portion of storage page.
AePruningBean Provides a facility for deleting data from the database.
AeStorageBean Bean for driving display of storage page.
AeUiDataBean A generic wrapper to contain UI form and other data.
AeWebUtil Utility class for common bean operations.
 

Package org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.web Description

This package contains java beans and supporting classes for driving the web app ui.
